des: Interested in finding out what is going on in Castine? Ask the Castine Concierge. You can find lodging, dining and attractions, along with checking the weather. For even more fun, enable the Baron of Castine skill to hear fun facts and history about the town.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
